175  const DynamicAny get(const std::string& name) const
176  {
177  NameVec::const_iterator it = _pNames->begin();
178  NameVec::const_iterator itEnd = _pNames->end();
179 
180  for(std::size_t counter = 0; it != itEnd; ++it, ++counter)
181  {
182  if (name == *it)
183  {
184  switch (counter)
185  {
186  case 0: return TupleType::template get<0>();
187  case 1: return TupleType::template get<1>();
188  case 2: return TupleType::template get<2>();
189  case 3: return TupleType::template get<3>();
190  case 4: return TupleType::template get<4>();
191  case 5: return TupleType::template get<5>();
192  case 6: return TupleType::template get<6>();
193  case 7: return TupleType::template get<7>();
194  case 8: return TupleType::template get<8>();
195  case 9: return TupleType::template get<9>();
196  case 10: return TupleType::template get<10>();
197  case 11: return TupleType::template get<11>();
198  case 12: return TupleType::template get<12>();
199  case 13: return TupleType::template get<13>();
200  case 14: return TupleType::template get<14>();
201  case 15: return TupleType::template get<15>();
202  case 16: return TupleType::template get<16>();
203  case 17: return TupleType::template get<17>();
204  case 18: return TupleType::template get<18>();
205  case 19: return TupleType::template get<19>();
206  default: throw RangeException();
207  }
208  }
209  }
210 
211  throw NotFoundException("Name not found: " + name);
212  }
213 
214  const DynamicAny operator [] (const std::string& name) const
215  {
216  return get(name);
217  }
218 
219  template<int N>
220  typename TypeGetter<N, Type>::ConstHeadType& get() const
221  {
222  return TupleType::template get<N>();
223  }
224 
225  template<int N>
226  typename TypeGetter<N, Type>::HeadType& get()

228  return TupleType::template get<N>();
229  }

231  template<int N>
232  void set(typename TypeGetter<N, Type>::ConstHeadType& val)
233  {
234  return TupleType::template set<N>(val);

237  const NameVecPtr& names()
238  {
239  return _pNames;
240  }
241 
242  void setName(std::size_t index, const std::string& name)
243  {
244  if (index >= _pNames->size())
245  throw InvalidArgumentException(format("Invalid index: %z", index));
246 
247  (*_pNames)[index] = name;
248  }
249 
250  const std::string& getName(std::size_t index)
251  {
252  if (index >= _pNames->size())
253  throw InvalidArgumentException(format("Invalid index: %z", index));
254 
255  return (*_pNames)[index];
256  }
257 
258  bool operator == (const NamedTuple& other) const
259  {
260  return TupleType(*this) == TupleType(other) && _pNames == other._pNames;
261  }
262 
263  bool operator != (const NamedTuple& other) const
264  {
265  return !(*this == other);
266  }
267 
268  bool operator < (const NamedTuple& other) const
269  {
270  TupleType th(*this);
271  TupleType oth(other);
272 
273  return (th < oth && _pNames == other._pNames) ||
274  (th == oth && _pNames < other._pNames) ||
275  (th < oth && _pNames < other._pNames);
276  }
277 
278 private:
279  void init(const std::string& n0 = "A",
280  const std::string& n1 = "B",
281  const std::string& n2 = "C",
282  const std::string& n3 = "D",
283  const std::string& n4 = "E",
284  const std::string& n5 = "F",
285  const std::string& n6 = "G",
286  const std::string& n7 = "H",
287  const std::string& n8 = "I",
288  const std::string& n9 = "J",
289  const std::string& n10 = "K",
290  const std::string& n11 = "L",
291  const std::string& n12 = "M",
292  const std::string& n13 = "N",
293  const std::string& n14 = "O",
294  const std::string& n15 = "P",
295  const std::string& n16 = "Q",
296  const std::string& n17 = "R",
297  const std::string& n18 = "S",
298  const std::string& n19 = "T")
299  {
300  if (!_pNames)
301  {
302  _pNames = new NameVec;
303  _pNames->push_back(n0);
304  _pNames->push_back(n1);
305  _pNames->push_back(n2);
306  _pNames->push_back(n3);
307  _pNames->push_back(n4);
308  _pNames->push_back(n5);
309  _pNames->push_back(n6);
310  _pNames->push_back(n7);
311  _pNames->push_back(n8);
312  _pNames->push_back(n9);
313  _pNames->push_back(n10);
314  _pNames->push_back(n11);
315  _pNames->push_back(n12);
316  _pNames->push_back(n13);
317  _pNames->push_back(n14);
318  _pNames->push_back(n15);
319  _pNames->push_back(n16);
320  _pNames->push_back(n17);
321  _pNames->push_back(n18);
322  _pNames->push_back(n19);
323  }
324  }
325 
326  NameVecPtr _pNames;
327 };

480  case 2: return TupleType::template get<2>();

2054  const DynamicAny get(const std::string& name) const
2055  {
2056  NameVec::const_iterator it = _pNames->begin();
2057  NameVec::const_iterator itEnd = _pNames->end();
2058 
2059  for(std::size_t counter = 0; it != itEnd; ++it, ++counter)
2060  {
2061  if (name == *it)
2062  {
2063  switch (counter)
2064  {
2065  case 0: return TupleType::template get<0>();
2066  case 1: return TupleType::template get<1>();
2067  case 2: return TupleType::template get<2>();
2068  case 3: return TupleType::template get<3>();
2069  case 4: return TupleType::template get<4>();
2070  case 5: return TupleType::template get<5>();
2071  case 6: return TupleType::template get<6>();
2072  case 7: return TupleType::template get<7>();
2073  case 8: return TupleType::template get<8>();
2074  case 9: return TupleType::template get<9>();
2075  case 10: return TupleType::template get<10>();
2076  case 11: return TupleType::template get<11>();
2077  case 12: return TupleType::template get<12>();
2078  default: throw RangeException();
2079  }
2080  }
2081  }
2082 
2083  throw NotFoundException("Name not found: " + name);
2084  }

4259  const NameVecPtr& names()
4260  {
4261  return _pNames;
4262  }
4263 
4264  void setName(std::size_t index, const std::string& name)
4265  {
4266  if (index >= _pNames->size())
4267  throw InvalidArgumentException(format("Invalid index: %z", index));
4268 
4269  (*_pNames)[index] = name;
4270  }
4271 
4272  const std::string& getName(std::size_t index)
4273  {
4274  if (index >= _pNames->size())
4275  throw InvalidArgumentException(format("Invalid index: %z", index));
4276 
4277  return (*_pNames)[index];
4278  }
4279 
4280  bool operator == (const NamedTuple& other) const
4281  {
4282  return TupleType(*this) == TupleType(other) && _pNames == other._pNames;
4283  }
4284 
4285  bool operator != (const NamedTuple& other) const
4286  {
4287  return !(*this == other);
4288  }
4289 
4290  bool operator < (const NamedTuple& other) const
4291  {
4292  TupleType th(*this);
4293  TupleType oth(other);
4294 
4295  return (th < oth && _pNames == other._pNames) ||
4296  (th == oth && _pNames < other._pNames) ||
4297  (th < oth && _pNames < other._pNames);
4298  }
4299 
4300 private:
4301  void init(const std::string& n0 = "A",
4302  const std::string& n1 = "B")
4303  {
4304  if (!_pNames)
4305  {
4306  _pNames = new NameVec;
4307  _pNames->push_back(n0);
4308  _pNames->push_back(n1);
4309  }
4310  }
4311 
4312  NameVecPtr _pNames;
4313 };

4316 template<class T0>
4317 struct NamedTuple<T0,NullTypeList>:
4318  public Tuple<T0>
4319 {
4320  typedef Tuple<T0> TupleType;
4321  typedef typename Tuple<T0>::Type Type;
4322 
4323  typedef std::vector<std::string> NameVec;
4324  typedef SharedPtr<NameVec> NameVecPtr;
4325 
4326  NamedTuple(): _pNames(0)
4327  {
4328  init();
4329  }
4330 
4331  NamedTuple(const NameVecPtr& rNames)
4332  {
4333  if (rNames->size() != TupleType::length)
4334  throw InvalidArgumentException("Wrong names vector length.");
4335 
4336  _pNames = rNames;
4337  }
4338 
4339  NamedTuple(typename TypeWrapper<T0>::CONSTTYPE& t0):
4340  TupleType(t0),
4341  _pNames(0)
4342  {
4343  init();
4344  }
4345 
4346  NamedTuple(const NameVecPtr& rNames,
4347  typename TypeWrapper<T0>::CONSTTYPE& t0):
4348  TupleType(t0)
4349  {
4350  if (rNames->size() != TupleType::length)
4351  throw InvalidArgumentException("Wrong names vector length.");
4352 
4353  _pNames = rNames;
4354  }
4355 
4356  NamedTuple(const std::string& n0, typename TypeWrapper<T0>::CONSTTYPE& t0):
4357  TupleType(t0),
4358  _pNames(0)
4359  {
4360  init(n0);
4361  }
4362 
4363  const DynamicAny get(const std::string& name) const
4364  {
4365  NameVec::const_iterator it = _pNames->begin();
4366  NameVec::const_iterator itEnd = _pNames->end();
4367 
4368  for(std::size_t counter = 0; it != itEnd; ++it, ++counter)
4369  {
4370  if (name == *it)
4371  {
4372  switch (counter)
4373  {
4374  case 0: return TupleType::template get<0>();
4375  default: throw RangeException();
4376  }
4377  }
4378  }
4379 
4380  throw NotFoundException("Name not found: " + name);
4381  }
4382 
4383  const DynamicAny operator [] (const std::string& name) const
4384  {
4385  return get(name);
4386  }
4387

4390  {
4391  return TupleType::template get<N>();
4392  }
4393

4396  {
4397  return TupleType::template get<N>();
4398  }
4399

4402  {
4403  return TupleType::template set<N>(val);
4404  }
4405 
4406  const NameVecPtr& names()
4407  {
4408  return _pNames;
4409  }
4410

4412  {
4413  if (index >= _pNames->size())
4414  throw InvalidArgumentException(format("Invalid index: %z", index));
4415 
4416  (*_pNames)[index] = name;
4417  }
4418

4420  {
4421  if (index >= _pNames->size())
4422  throw InvalidArgumentException(format("Invalid index: %z", index));
4423 
4424  return (*_pNames)[index];
4425  }
4426 
4427  bool operator == (const NamedTuple& other) const
4428  {
4429  return TupleType(*this) == TupleType(other) && _pNames == other._pNames;
4430  }
4431 
4432  bool operator != (const NamedTuple& other) const
4433  {
4434  return !(*this == other);
4435  }
4436 
4437  bool operator < (const NamedTuple& other) const
4438  {

4440  TupleType oth(other);
4441 
4442  return (th < oth && _pNames == other._pNames) ||
4443  (th == oth && _pNames < other._pNames) ||
4444  (th < oth && _pNames < other._pNames);
4445  }

4449  {
4450  if (!_pNames)
4451  {
4452  _pNames = new NameVec;
4453  _pNames->push_back(n0);
4454  }
4455  }
